Controlling Unit
-------------------------
Function:       Controlling Microcontroller Board
Element:        Arduino Mega 2560
Product Link:   http://arduino.cc/en/Main/arduinoBoardMega2560)


Function:       Controlling Unit Shield - connect controller with armband modules
Element:        self designed PCB with connectors to connect armband modules and 
                Bluetooth interface for connection to the smartphone 
                (Higher Order Controll Unit) device
  Shield PCB
  Details:        see pcb file

  Bluetooth Interface
  Element:        Red Bear Lab BLE Mini (Bluetooth Low Energy)
  Product Link:   http://redbearlab.com/blemini/
  Chip Datasheet: https://redbearlab.com/s/RBT01BLEModulev10.pdf


