Temperature
-------------------------
Name:           Module Controller[1]

Function:       Temperature Stimulation Element
Element:        Vktech TEC1-12706 Peltier
Shop Link:      http://www.amazon.de/gp/product/B00J5BKU0A
Datasheet:      www.hebeiltd.com.cn/peltier.datasheet/TEC1-12706.pdf

Function:       Peltier Controller
Element:        DC Dual Motor Driver 30V 4A v2
Product Link:   http://www.microbot.it/en/product/73/DC-Dual-Motor-Driver-30V-4A-V2.html
H-Bridge Chip:  L298
Chip Datasheet: http://www.st.com/web/en/resource/technical/document/datasheet/CD00000240.pdf

Function:       Temperature Sensore
Element:        InLine Temperature Sensor / NTC 10kOhm
Shop Link:      http://www.amazon.de/gp/product/B001IQ0L2M

Function:       Temperature Digitalzation
Element:        Adafruit ADS1115 16-Bit ADC
Product Link:   https://www.adafruit.com/products/1085
I2C ADC Chip:   ADS1115
Chip Datasheet: http://www.adafruit.com/datasheets/ads1115.pdf



